61
00:10:15.420 --> 00:10:22.249
Jannik Luhn: Or at least an example spec, because decryptors, they might have different interfaces.

62
00:10:22.570 --> 00:10:37.820
Jannik Luhn: And, then for, in particular, the testnet, we probably want to have some example decryptors, live. Again, different variants, maybe TE, maybe threshold-based, and also centralized ones, maybe, for testing.

63
